    <p>What is Shopping Advisor System (SAS)?</p>
    <p>The project develops a software application, Shopping Advisor System. This project is targets 2 main audiences, retailers and consumers. The purpose of this system is to help retailers to manage inventory levels and recommend the potential items that available in the market but not selling in the store. For consumers, this system able to acts as real grocery staff that helps user to look for items easily. This system would recommend user other items that he or she might like.
	  The proposed solution system consists of 4 modules, inventory control, stock recommendation, product categorisation, and product recommendation. The project module integrates each other to form a software application that capable to help retailers and consumers.
